snippet.title: Best VGM 1818 - Super Win the Game - Razor's Edge
snippet.description:
OST: https://piratehearts.bandcamp.com/album/super-win-the-game-soundtrack

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC
Super Win the Game (2014)
Razor's Edge
J. Kyle Pittman
